name: Liminal-Backrooms Multiplayer
description:
Fall in this Halloween. Find other corpses of players that failed. Multiplayer persistent universe. Leave behind clues or find clues from other players to pass certain areas. 10 entities and 11 items to help you along the way. Trade with Roman or other players and use items to find your way out.

Game uses a custom raytraced solution for global illumination for realistic spooky dark rooms!

Server is located in central USA for maximum latency for east and west coast.
